original_title: Jack Bruce & Robin Trower - Seven Moons Live 2009
overview: Two legends, one hour of fearsome axe-wielding! They do virtually the entire Seven Moons album plus signature tunes from Bruce's famous catalog, all filmed at the majestic Concertgebouw De Vereeniging in the Netherlands in 5.1 Surround Sound. Tracks include Lives Of Clay; Perfect Place; White Room; Politician and more!
title: Jack Bruce & Robin Trower - Seven Moons Live 2009
